            "description": "<p>The floating gem flares with inner radiance, sending out beams of light to captivate and drain the vitality from all who approach.</p>",
            "disable": "<p>@Check[arcana|dc:35] (expert), @Check[occultism|dc:35] (expert), or @Check[religion|dc:35] (expert) to unravel the magical matrix within the gem, @Check[crafting|dc:40] or @Check[thievery|dc:40] check to unbalance the crystal's alignment, or a @Check[athletics|dc:43] check to damage one of the gem's facets and change its geometry; two successes are required to disable the hazard</p>",
