            "reset": "",
            "routine": "<p>(3 actions) The captivating gem attempts uses all three of its actions to incapacitate creatures. It targets the closest creature with its Freezing Light ability, then a different creature with its facet flare Strike. If a creature has already been @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Paralyzed] by Freezing Light, it chooses a different target for that ability.</p>"
